These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, drama, superhero, documentary
There 4 different types of food: papaya, apple, cauliflower, peas
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, juice, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, skiing, ice-hockey
 1. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking cola is the person eating apple##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
 6. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
 7. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
10. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person watching spy movies##7
11. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
12. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary    | drama | superhero    | spy   |
| Food   | papaya | cauliflower | apple | peas |
| Beverage           | tea       | juice   | cola  | hot-chocolate     |
| Sport     | skateboarding      | skiing   | ice-hockey    | baseball    |

