.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, milk, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, airplane, bike
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, light-blue, lavender, white
4 different pets are kept: snake, horse, bird, turtle
 1. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 2. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
 3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
 4. the owner of the bird is the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
 6. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person who likes yellow##7
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
10. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
11. the person who likes light-blue is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage          | soy-milk   | milk       | coffee    | iced-tea      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike | taxi         | airplane   |
| Color   | white   | yellow  | light-blue       | lavender |
| Pet         | snake      | bird  | turtle | horse |

