There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, juice, fanta
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person traveling to nizza##7
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the victorian house##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 5. the palace house is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
 6. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
 8. the person traveling to nizza is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
12. the modern house is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Birthday           | february | july | september | june |
| City   | venice        | marseilles    | san-francisco    | nizza    |
| House   | palace        | craftsman   | victorian   | modern         |
| Beverage           | coffee          | cola       | fanta   | juice           |

