 4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
 6. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person who likes azure and the person who likes green##7
 8. the person playing domino is not the person who likes azure##6
 9. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Game         | billiard      | mah-jongg   | domino   | scrabble       |
| Birthday   | february | september    | november | march       |
| Transport   | roller  | ship | tram   | motorbike     |
| Color         | azure   | grey    | green   | orange |

