.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, train, taxi, skateboard
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, light-blue, yellow, white
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, badminton, biathlon, cycling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, mystery, sports, romance
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching sports movies##2
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is not the person watching mystery movies##6
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person who likes white##7
 8. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
10. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
11. the person driving the car is the person who likes yellow##1
12. the person who likes yellow is not the person watching sports movies##6

