.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, lilac, black, azure
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, comedy, satire, superhero
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia, orchid, daffodil
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, canadian, polish, egyptian
 1. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
 2. the person watching satire movies is the person who likes black##1
 3. the canadian is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is between the person who likes azure and the person who likes lilac##2
 5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5
 6. the person who growsiris is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person who likes yellow##7
 7. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
 8. the person who growsiris is the malaysian##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
10. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
11. the polish is in an even position##4
12. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color   | azure      | black     | lilac   | yellow    |
| Movie-Genre     | superhero | satire   | comedy | documentary |
| Flower     | daffodil        | orchid     | iris  | zinnia      |
| Nationality   | canadian       | egyptian | malaysian   | polish    |

 